{
  "stem": "7282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Imagine, after the war-- during the war, when we're-- when, when the Germans runned back, my friend-- he is in the picture, J.D.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Katz-- he was lieutenant in the-- in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got into-- with his company into Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was after the war already, or what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I wouldn't go-- I wouldn't go for, for no money there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans-- well, you can't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you can't judge everyone the same.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is different people, different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe they're pretending to be, what, but they are different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like, I was in Germany for two years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Since '44 up to '46, I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had established there, too, a factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Germans used to work for me there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of them were OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some of them, they took me up to their house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "By chance-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by chance, the owner from the house left pictures on the table.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I happened to look them over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I've seen what they sent from the front, how they killed the Jews on the pictures.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was their pictures on the-- on, on, on the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I couldn't take them because I couldn't steal them, or what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was on the table.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I, I, I could imagine what kind of people-- what they, they, they were, or what.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you can't judge everyone on the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some was nice people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people were even-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so you want me to finish?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm finished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some, some people were good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They even-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] about those people there, even though they were Germans, they kept some people-- Jewish people on the lagers.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
